415
00:18:13,530 --> 00:18:14,369
and you can go home.

416
00:18:15,329 --> 00:18:16,569
Is that okay, Mrs. Zhang?

417
00:18:16,970 --> 00:18:18,450
Sure.

418
00:18:18,569 --> 00:18:19,849
