489
00:20:09,530 --> 00:20:10,379
You want a fight?

490
00:20:10,380 --> 00:20:11,890
Whoever starts the fight
is in the wrong.

491
00:20:11,890 --> 00:20:13,804
When the Shen family begs us
for reconciliation,

492
00:20:13,810 --> 00:20:15,493
