495
00:20:18,569 --> 00:20:20,290
your sister.

496
00:20:20,290 --> 00:20:21,290
Think carefully.

497
00:20:21,290 --> 00:20:21,930
You can hit me,

498
00:20:21,930 --> 00:20:23,271
but you can't touch my sister.

499
00:20:23,290 --> 00:20:24,889
- My pitiful son.
- Understood?

500
00:20:25,137 --> 00:20:25,880
It's tough for you.

501
00:20:25,889 --> 00:20:26,450
Go.

502
00:20:30,809 --> 00:20:31,649
